# Shared VHS settings for all ratatui-interact demos
# Usage: Source settings.tape (from other tape files in this directory)

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set CursorBlink false
